                     <interp inst="t18260216-103-person740" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I searched the prisoner, and found three shillings in his pocket; I pulled off his high-shoe, with some difficulty, and found half-a-crown in it - he said it slipped there out of his breeches-pocket, but that could not be, for the pocket was sound.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The money was all my own.</p>
